ed%20by%20the%20Stalin-led%20government.%20Further%2C%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20moved%20a%20resolution%20which%20irked%20the%20governor%20and%20he%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Assembly%20before%20the%20national%20anthem%20was%20played%20in%20the%20end%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Ftn-governor-skips-portions-dravidian-leaders-and-ambedkar-speech-cm-objects-171717%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EPast%20conflicts%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20the%20DMK%20government%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20protested%20against%20Ravi%20as%20the%3Cem%3E%20PTI%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-politics%2Ftamil-nadu-vs-tamilagam-governor-rn-ravi-row-dmk-8368892%2F%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20him%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CHere%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20narrative%20has%20been%20created.%20Everything%20applicable%20for%20the%20whole%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20say%20no.%20It%20has%20become%20a%20habit.%20So%20many%20theses%20have%20been%20written%20%E2%80%93%20all%20false%20and%20poor%20fiction.%20This%20must%20be%20broken.%20Truth%20must%20prevail.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Last%20year%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20governor%20also%20objected%20to%20the%20state%20administration%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Condriya%20arasu%E2%80%9D%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Frn-ravi-dmk-tamil-term-union-govt-8376233%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707741059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-cont