nleashed%20a%20barrage%20of%20sarcastic%20taunts%2C%20dubbing%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20%26quot%3Bpalturam%26quot%3B%20and%20questioning%20whether%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-meets-pm-narendra-modi-says-will-never-leave-nda-again-5014220%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFollowing%2520his%2520meeting%2520with%2520PM%2Cpolitical%2520issues%2520related%2520to%2520Bihar.%26amp%3Btext%3DNItish%2520Kumar%2520said%252C%2520%2522Never%2520now%2C(in%2520the%2520NDA)%2522.%5C%22%3EPM%20Modi%20could%20guarantee%20that%20Nitish%20would%20not%20backtrack%20again%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20trust%20vote%20became%20necessary%20as%20Nitish%2C%20the%20orchestrator%20of%20the%20opposition%20I.N.D.I.A%20bloc%2C%20in%20a%20surprising%20move%2C%20made%20a%20U-turn%20and%20rejoined%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-chief-minister-nitish-kumar-says-will-stay-permanently-with-nda-now-5020268%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20NDA%20last%20month%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20classic%20Nitish%20style%2C%20this%20somersault%20was%20executed%20with%20finesse%20and%20ease%2C%20with%20his%20resignation%20from%20Mahagathbandhan%20and%20swearing-in%20as%20NDA%20Chief%20Minister%20occurring%20within%20a%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ENitish's%20Move%20May%20Weaken%20Bihar%20BJP%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nitish's%20return%20strengthens%20BJP's%20'Mission%20400'%20bid%20for%202024%2C%20it%20weakens%20the%20local%20unit's%20attempts%20to%20gain%20a%20foothold%20in%20the%20state%20without%20relying%20on%20Nitish.%20Social%20media%20had%20a%20field%20day%2C%20flooded%20with%20memes%20about%20%26quot%3Bpalturam's%26quot%3B%20latest%20flip-flop.%20One%20meme%20that%20caught%20my%20eye%20humorously%20stated%20that%20in%20Bihar%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20resigns%2C%20but%20it%20is%20the%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20who%20lose%20their%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20declared%20a%20'Mission%2050%25%20vote%20share'%20target%20and%20a%20'Mission%20400%2B%20seats'%20tally%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20aims%20to%20break%20the%20record%20of%20404%20seats%20achieved%20by%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20in%201984.%20With%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20bloc%20failing%20to%20take%20off%2C%20the%20opposition%20in%20disarray%2C%20hurdles%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks%2C%20and%20a%20positive%2C%20emotionally%20charged%20environment%20created%20in%20the%20country%20after%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20the%20BJP%20senses%20an%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)'s%20(JD-U)%20return%20to%20the%20NDA%20fold%20also%20neutralises%2C%20to%20a%20large%20extent%2C%20the%20narrative%20that%20allies%20are%20leaving%20the%20BJP.%20With%20the%20JD(U)'s%20re-entry%2C%20the%20NDA's%20seat%20tally%20is%20back%20to%20around%20350%20seats%2C%20close%20to%20the%202019%20tally%20of%20353.%20The%20ruling%20alliance%20now%20needs%20just%2050%20more%20seats%20to%20cross%20the%20magical%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EA%20Rainbow%20Coalition%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Nitish%20back%20in%20the%20fold%2C%20NDA%20is%20expected%20to%20repeat%20its%202019%20tally%20of%2039%20seats%20out%20of%2040%2C%20as%20shown%20by%20a%20latest%20NDTV%20survey.%20Without%20the%20JD(U)%2C%20surveys%20predicted%20a%20loss%20of%20around%2015%20seats.%20According%20to%20the%20survey%2C%2053%25%20of%20respondents%20are%20likely%20to%20back%20NDA%2C%20while%20only%2023%25%20favour%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20bloc%2C%20with%2018%25%20respondents%20undecided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20Nitish%20had%20stayed%20with%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20bloc%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20a%20dead%20heat%2C%20with%2035%25%20of%20respondents%20backing%20both%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%2C%20with%2020%25%20undecided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20now%20boasts%20a%20rainbow%20coalition%20of%20upper%20caste%2C%20Kurmi%2FKoeri%2C%20Most%20Backward%20Classes%20(MBCs)%2C%20Mahadalits%2C%20and%20Paswans%2C%20which%20account%20for%20roughly%2060%25-65%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population.%20Party%20strategists%20believe%20there%20is%20still%20scope%20for%20gaining%2016%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20one%20in%20Bihar%2C%20two%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20two%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20one%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20one%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20totalling%2023%20seats%20in%20North%20India%2C%20helped%20by%20the%20fervour%20around%20Ram%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20readmitting%20Nitish%20Kumar%20deals%20a%20blow%20of%20sorts%20to%20the%20BJP's%20ambitions%20of%20strengthening%20the%20party%20on%20a%20standalone%20basis%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20party%20had%20appointed%20the%20firebrand%20young%20leader%20from%20the%20Koeri%20community%2C%20Samrat%20Chaudhary%2C%20to%20lead%20the%20brigade%20and%20develop%20the%20party%20base%2C%20aiming%20to%20weaken%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20hold%20on%20a%20section%20of%20lower%20OBCs.%20With%20the%20induction%20of%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20it%20hoped%20to%20develop%20new%20leadership%20amongst%20Mahadalits.%20Nitish's%20return%20into%20the%20NDA%20just%201.5%20years%20ahead%20of%20state%20elections%20next%20year%20derails%20those%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EVoters%20May%20Get%20Confused%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202020%20state%20elections%2C%20Nitish%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20strategically%20placed%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP)%20candidates%20in%20its%20seats%20to%20weaken%20him%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20JD(U)%20bagging%20just%2043%20seats%2C%20a%20decrease%20of%2028.%20Data%20shows%20the%20LJP%20damaged%20JD(U)'s%20prospects%20in%2030%20odd%20seats%2C%20which%20was%20one%20of%20the%20bones%20of%20contention%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20and%20a%20prime%20reason%20why%20Nitish%20left%20the%20NDA%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20could%20send%20confusing%20signals%20to%20its%20core%20voters%2C%20an%20admission%20perhaps%20that%20the%20BJP%20doesn't%20have%20leaders%20to%20match%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20popularity%20and%20charisma%20in%20Bihar.%20Today%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20is%20the%20clear%20number-two%20leader%20who%20is%20young%2C%20dynamic%2C%20and%20has%20administrative%20experience%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MGB%20got%20a%2037%25%20vote%20share%20in%20the%202020%20state%20elections%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20NDA's%2C%20falling%20eight%20seats%20short%20of%20the%20majority.%20Had%20Congress%20performed%20better%20(it%20had%20the%20worst%20strike%20rate%20of%2027%25%2C%20winning%20just%2019%20of%20the%2070%20allocated%20seats)%2C%20MGB%20would%20have%20done%20much%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Question%20of%20Accommodating%20Nitish%20At%20Centre%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20specifics%20of%20the%20deal%20are%20not%20public.%20Will%20Nitish%20continue%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20till%202025%3F%20Will%20the%202025%20state%20elections%20be%20fought%20under%20his%20leadership%3F%20Will%20the%20BJP%20want%20him%20to%20step%20down%20and%20project%20its%20own%20CM%20face%3F%20Easing%20out%20Nitish%20before%202025%20and%20adjusting%20him%20at%20the%20Centre%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20easy%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Ckissa%20kursi%20ka%E2%80%9D.%20Why%20would%20he%20want%20to%20be%20an%20inconsequential%20minister%20under%20Modi%20at%20the%20Centre%20when%20he%20could%20be%20the%20king%20of%20a%20state%20with%20less%20intervention%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar's%20return%20indicates%20short-term%20gains%20for%20the%20BJP%20but%20comes%20with%20possible%20long-term%20pain.%20Will%20there%20be%20yet%20another%20realignment%20after%20short-term%20gains%20realised%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3