0%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20you%20legislating%20on%20this%3F%20Why%20bring%20in%20the%20executive%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FTNO3CrgdAN0%3Fsi%3DRz6VjRhhGF1wlneB%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Lokur%20identified%20several%20instances%20when%20the%20UCC%20will%20lead%20to%20harassment%20of%20innocent%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Justice%20Lokur%20said%20the%20requirement%20to%20register%20a%20live-in%20relationship%20within%20one%20month%20is%20simply%20harassment.%20He%20said%20%E2%80%9Cjail%20is%20too%20much%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20register%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20instance%20of%20harassment%20is%20the%20clause%20which%20says%20the%20Registrar%20can%20deny%20permission%20for%20a%20live-in%20relationship.%20Justice%20Lokur%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20strange%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20kind%20of%20enquiry%20will%20the%20Registrar%20conduct%3F%E2%80%9D%20For%20instance%2C%20he%20asked%2C%20how%20will%20the%20Registrar%20establish%20that%20the%20two%20people%20are%20not%20previously%20married%3F%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20is%20no%20provision%20for%20appeal%20if%20permission%20is%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20instance%20of%20harassment%20will%20arise%20because%20the%20Registrar%20has%20a%20duty%20to%20inform%20the%20local%20police%20station.%20Justice%20Lokur%20said%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20have%20they%20(the%20police)%20got%20to%20do%20with%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20another%20instance%20of%20harassment%20will%20be%20the%20requirement%20that%20if%20any%20of%20the%20partners%20is%20under%20the%20age%20of%2021%20their%20parents%20must%20be%20informed.%20Justice%20Lokur%20asked%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20the%20permission%20of%20parents%20needed%20(if%20both%20are%20over%20the%20age%20of%2018%20and%20adults)%3F%E2%80%9D%20In%20India%2C%20an%20individual%20over%2018%20is%20an%20adult%20and%20does%20not%20need%20parental%20permission%20for%20what%20he%20or%20she%20chooses%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20egregious%20opportunity%20for%20harassment%20arises%20out%20of%20Section%20386%20which%20allows%20any%20third%20party%20to%20submit%20a%20complaint%20that%20a%20live-in%20relationship%20has%20not%20been%20registered.%20Justice%20Lokur%20agreed%20this%20would%20lead%20to%20moral%20policing%20and%20reprehensible%20vigilantism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumming%20up%20the%20different%20instances%20of%20potential%20harassment%20that%20would%20arise%20out%20of%20the%20UCC%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20of%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20Justice%20Lokur%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9Cit%20can%20become%20an%20instrument%20of%20harassment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Lokur%20did%20not%20accept%20the%20explanation%20given%20by%20unnamed%20officials%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20is%20necessary%20because%20of%20%E2%80%9Cheinous%20crime%20among%20live-in%20couples%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20accept%20this%20%E2%80%A6%20there%20is%20no%20data%20for%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20substantial%20section%20of%20the%20interview%2C%20Justice%20Lokur%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20UCC%20flagrantly%20breaches%20the%202017%20%3Cem%3EPuttaswamy%3C%2Fem%3E%20case%20judgement%20declaring%20privacy%20to%20be%20a%20fundamental%20right.%20Justice%20Lokur%20identified%20several%20areas%20where%20the%20law%20on%20privacy%20is%20breached.%20These%20include%20the%20need%20for%20registration%2C%20informing%20the%20police%2C%20parental%20permission%2C%20the%20need%20for%20enquiry%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20neighbours%20have%20to%20be%20satisfied.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Justice%20Lokur%20asked%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20is%20the%20privacy%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Justice%20Lokur%20said%20he%20has%20no%20doubt%20that%20if%20challenged%20the%20entire%20section%20of%20the%20Uttarakhand%20UCC%20on%20live-in%20relationships%20would%20be%20scrapped.%20He%20said%20it%20violates%20both%20Articles%2021%20and%2014%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707739236000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12170819%2Fkt-12-feb.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Futtarakhand-ucc-a-bad-law-arbitrary-will-lead-to-huge-harassment-likely-to-be-scrapped%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20Madan%20Lokur%20said%20that%20at%20least%20four%20or%20five%20of%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code's%20stipulations%20regarding%20live-in%20relationships%20will%20cause%20'huge%20harassment%20of%20innocent%20people'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Futtarakhand-ucc-a-bad-law-arbitrary-will-lead-to-huge-harassment-likely-to-be-scrapped%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20popular%20economist%20says%20there's%20no%20separation%20between%20work%20and%20play%20anymore%20because%20everything%20Gen%20Z%20does%20is%20Googleable%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222688%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20scrolls%20through%20a%20social%20media%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c9e3bb610ab33aa5deebb3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BThey%20get%20much%20older%2C%20much%20faster%20as%20a%20result%20of%20living%20in%20a%20social%20media%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Yanis%20Varoufakis%20said%20of%20Gen%20Z.%20%3Cp%3EClaire%20S