0when%20he%20could%20not%20present%20any%20identification%20to%20US%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Evening%20Standard%20reported%20that%20Sturt%20was%20returned%20to%20the%20UK%20and%20charged%20on%20suspicion%20of%20fraud%20and%20aviation%20security%20offenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Sun%2C%20the%20security%20breach%20has%20led%20to%20the%20UK's%20Home%20Office%20seeking%20answers%20as%20to%20how%20such%20an%20incident%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Office%20declined%20a%20Business%20Insider%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20referring%20the%20request%20to%20London's%20Metropolitan%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20Home%20Office%20told%20the%20Evening%20Standard%20that%20%26quot%3Bheads%20will%20roll.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unnamed%20source%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20staggering%20this%20could%20happen.%20It%20doesn't%20bear%20thinking%20about%20what%20might%20have%20happened%20if%20a%20terrorist%20had%20successfully%20boarded%20a%20flight%20undetected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20embarrassment%26quot%3B%20for%20Heathrow%2C%20the%20UK's%20border%20officials%2C%20and%20British%20Airways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20a%20BA%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20airline%20is%20%26quot%3Bassisting%20the%20authorities%20with%20their%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Heathrow%20spokesperson%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAll%20people%20who%20go%20airside%20are%20subject%20to%20security%20screening%2C%20including%20the%20individual%20involved%20in%20this%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20supporting%20the%20authorities%20with%20their%20ongoing%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20incident%2C%20Thames%20Valley%20Police%20issued%20an%20alert%20for%20Sturt%2C%20who%20went%20missing%20from%20a%20hospital%20where%20he%20was%20being%20treated%20on%20m