%2F2024%2F02%2F12170629%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-12-at-5.04.51-PM-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696783%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFarmers%20preparing%20to%20leave%20for%20the%20protest.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECondemning%20the%20Haryana%20government%E2%80%99s%20action%20against%20farmers%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20Manjit%20Singh%20Rai%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20should%20remember%20that%20we%20are%20the%20citizens%20of%20this%20country%20and%20want%20to%20reach%20Delhi%20to%20raise%20our%20demands.%20We%20are%20not%20coming%20from%20Pakistan%20or%20the%20Taliban.%20Why%20is%20the%20Modi%20government%20afraid%20of%20farmers%3F%20It%20is%20a%20totally%20unjust%20attitude.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20allegations%20that%20the%20farmers%20were%20instigated%20by%20opposition%20leaders%20to%20conduct%20the%20protest%2C%20Manjit%20Singh%20Rai%20said%20farmers%20were%20raising%20their%20voice%20for%20themselves.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20left%20on%20our%20own%20to%20fight%20for%20our%20rights.%20How%20did%20the%20opposition%20come%20into%20this%20picture%3F%20Our%20question%20is%20that%20if%20the%20Modi%20government%20can%20waive%20off%20the%20loans%20of%20corporate%20houses%2C%20then%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20they%20do%20away%20with%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20loans%3F%20The%20Modi%20government%20should%20remember%20that%20farmers%20across%20the%20world%20were%20uniting%20against%20the%20corporate%20houses%20and%20everywhere%20the%20governments%20had%20to%20bow%20before%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20voice.%20Look%20how%20Europe%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20were%20on%20the%20roads%20after%20taking%20inspiration%20from%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20last%20time%20too%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20apologised%20to%20the%20farmers%20for%20passing%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%2C%20and%20this%20time%20also%20they%20will%20apologise%20to%20the%20farmers%20for%20not%20fulfilling%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20had%20also%20cornered%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20asked%20them%20not%20to%20create%20another%20border%20between%20Punjab%20and%20India.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20as%20many%20barbed%20wires%20placed%20from%20Haryana%20to%20Delhi%20as%20there%20are%20at%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20border%20with%20Pakistan.%20The%20Union%20government%20should%20accept%20the%20legitimate%20demands%20of%20the%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Tarn%20Taran%20district%20near%20Amritsar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12170452%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-12-at-3.12.25-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12170452%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-12-at-3.12.25-PM.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12170452%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-12-at-3.12.25-PM-300x193.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12170452%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-12-at-3.12.25-PM-1024x657.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696781%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22693%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBarricades%20put%20up%20by%20the%20Haryana%20government.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20en%20route%20Delhi%2C%20BKU%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20spokesperson%20Tejveer%20Singh%20Ambala%20also%20said%20that%20%E2%80%98Godi%20media%E2%80%99%20will%20never%20show%20how%20farmers%20are%20moving%20in%20a%2