ystematic%20sexual%20exploitation.%20The%20man%20in%20question%2C%20Zilla%20Parishad%20member%20Sheikh%20Shajahan%20--%20also%20accused%20of%20land%20grabbing%20--%20is%20on%20the%20run.%20He%20is%20also%20wanted%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20PDS%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeshkhali%2C%20an%20island%20in%20Sundarbans%20close%20to%20the%20Bangladesh%20border%2C%20has%20been%20placed%20under%20Prohibitory%20Orders%20banning%20large%20gatherings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYoung%20Hindu%20married%20women%20are%20being%20deliberately%20targetted%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Irani%20alleged%2C%20reading%20out%20what%20she%20said%20were%20the%20women's%20version%20of%20events%20as%20told%20to%20the%20local%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20%26quot%3Bwill%20now%20allow%20her%20men%20to%20pick%20out%20young%20Hindu%20married%20women%20to%20be%20raped%20night%20after%20night%20in%20the%20TMC%20office%20cannot%20be%20articulated%20in%20mere%20words.%20Can%20we%20as%20citizens%20be%20mute%20spectators%3F'%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20days%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20women%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20armed%20with%20sticks%20and%20brooms%2C%20have%20been%20holding%20protests%2C%20alleging%20that%20Sheikh%20Shajahan%20and%20his%20%26quot%3Bgang%26quot%3B%20have%20captured%20swathes%20of%20land%20by%20force%2C%20and%20are%20sexually%20exploiting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20unverified%20by%20NDTV%2C%20that's%20being%20widely%20circulated%20online%2C%20a%20woman%20alleged%20that%20they%20are%20being%20dragged%20off%20to%20the%20Trinamool%20office%2C%20kept%20overnight%20and%20sexually%20assaulted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20have%20demanded%20the%20arrest%20of%20Sheikh%20Shajahan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20on%20the%20run%20since%20a%20team%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20went%20to%20raid%20his%20house%20last%20month%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20ra