0for%20seven%20years%2C%20till%20their%20break%20up%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20on%20the%20show%2C%20Ankita%20Lokhande%20was%20severely%20criticised%20for%20talking%20about%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%2C%20who%20died%20in%202020.%20Explaining%20that%20she%20only%20spoke%20about%20the%20late%20star%20in%20a%20positive%20light%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fankita-lokhande-on-talking-about-sushant-singh-rajput-in-bigg-boss-17-kisi-ki-permission-ki-koi-zarurat-nahi-5018035%5C%22%3EAnkita%20Lokhande%20told%20ETimes%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20read%20about%20it%20and%20I%20would%20like%20to%20say%20that%20I%20don't%20need%20anyone's%20fan%20following%20and%20%3Cem%3Emujhe%20kisi%20ke%20baare%20mein%20baat%20karne%20ke%20liye%20bhi%20kisi%20ki%20permission%20ki%20koi%20zarurat%20nahi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BI%20don't%20need%20anyone's%20permission%20to%20talk%5D.%20If%20someone%20has%20done%20something%20really%20nice%20in%20their%20life%2C%20I%20would%20definitely%20discuss%20it.%20I%20used%20to%20discuss%20my%20father%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20Bigg%20Boss%2017%20house%20because%20I%20felt%20he%20was%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20my%20life.%20Yes%2C%20I%20discussed%20Sushant%20as%20well%3Cem%3E%20kyunki%20agar%20mere%20saamne%20koi%20ladka%20baitha%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20he%20wants%20to%20be%20like%20his%20inspiration%20Sushant%20and%20if%20I%20know%20about%20Sushant%20then%20why%20won't%20I%20speak%20or%20share%20information.%20I%20will%20definitely%20motivate%20that%20person.%20%3Cem%3EAgar%20koi%20insaan%20chala%20gaya%20aur%20usne%20bahut%20acchi%20cheezein%20ki%20hai%20life%20mein%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BIf%20someone%2C%20who%20has%20passed%20away%2C%20has%20done%20good%20things%20in%20his%20lifetime%5D%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20problem%20discussing%2C%20mere%20husband%20ko%20koi%20problem%20nahi%20hai%2C%20I'm%20not%20answerable%20to%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkita%20Lokhande%20and%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%20me