0all%20stopped%20once%20I%20came%20(to%20power)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20for%2015%20years%2C%20I%20took%20up%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20worked%20for%20every%20level%20of%20society%2C%20for%20their%20development.%20%E2%80%A6Law%20and%20order%20has%20improved%3A%20women%20roam%20around%20till%20late%20at%20night.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20they%20came%20again%2C%20they%20just%20continued%20my%20policies%20and%20initiatives%2C%20and%20are%20now%20trying%20to%20take%20credit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20opposition%20walked%20out%2C%20Tejashwi%20spoke%20in%20the%20assembly%20and%20hit%20out%20at%20Nitish.%20What%20is%20the%20guarantee%20he%20won%E2%80%99t%20swap%20sides%20again%2C%20the%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20asked%3A%20%E2%80%9CCan%20PM%20Modi%20guarantee%20that%20Nitish%20won%E2%80%99t%20switch%20camps%20again%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20%5BNitish%5D%20came%20out%20of%20Raj%20Bhavan%20after%20resigning%2C%20you%20said%20%E2%80%9D%3Cem%3Emann%20nhi%20lag%20raha%20tha%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6%20hum%20log%20nachne%20gaane%20ke%20liye%20thode%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(you%20said%20you%20weren%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%98enjoying%20it%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6%20are%20we%20there%20to%20entertain%20you)%3F%20We%20were%20there%20to%20support%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20but%20he%20took%20oath%20thrice%20in%20a%20single%20term.%20This%20is%20something%20we%20never%20saw%20before.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMLAs%20from%20the%20RJD%2C%20Congress%20and%20Left%20Front%20all%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707734057000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28163221%2F400924413_926965212122173_7713585483950685171_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-opposition-walks-out-of-assembly-nitish-kumar-wins-trust-vote-in-bihar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MLAs%20from%20the%20RJD%2C%20Congress%20and%20Left%20Front%20all%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20assembly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-opposition-walks-out-of-assembly-nitish-kumar-wins-trust-vote-in-bihar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20McDonald's%20franchisee%20is%20paying%20%244.35%20million%20to%20settle%20a%20lawsuit%20from%20a%20worker%20who%20said%20she%20was%20raped%20by%20her%20manager%20when%20she%20was%20just%2014%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McDonald's%20franchisees%20are%20upset%20by%20new%20royalty%20hike%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6511a7bb59fd710019effadf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20McDonald's%20franchise%20group%20criticizes%20McDonald's%20for%20royalty%20fee%20hike.%20%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20McDonald's%20worker%20in%20Pittsburgh%20said%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20she%20was%20raped%20by%20her%20manager%20when%20she%20was%2014.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lawsuit%20says%20her%20employer%20didn't%20take%20action%20after%20she%20tried%20to%20report%20the%20harassment%20she%20experienced.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMcDonald's%20franchisee%20Rice%20Enterprises%20is%20paying%C2%A0%244.35%20million%20to%20settle%20the%20suit%2C%20first%20filed%20in%202021.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20McDonald's%20franchisee%20has%20agreed%20to%20pay%20%244.35%20million%20to%20settle%20a%20lawsuit%20from%20a%20worker%20in%20Pittsburgh%20who%20said%20she%20was%20raped%20by%20her%20manager%2C%20a%20registered%20sex%20offender%2C%20when%20she%20was%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20reached%20a%20settlement%20last%20Monday.%20The%20minor's%20family%20had%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20both%20McDonald's%20and%20Rice%20Enterprises%2C%20the%20eight-unit%20franchise%20business%20operating%20the%20restaurant%20she%20worked%20at%2C%20in%20September%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20accused%20McDonald's%20and%20Rice%20Enterprises%20of%20failing%20to%20train%20the%20minor%20on%20how%20to%20identify%20and%20report%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20perform%20background%20checks%20on%20the%20manager%2C%20and%20properly%20address%20complaints%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20abuse%20made%20by%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald%E2%80%99s%20was%20released%20from%20any%20legal%20claims%20on%20the%20topic%20and%20was%20not%20a%20signatory%20on%20the%20settlement%2C%20which%20was%20reached%20between%20the%20minor%E2%80%99s%20family%20and%20Rice%20Enterprises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20minor%2C%20who%20wasn't%20named%20in%20the%20legal%20filings%2C%20started%20working%20at%20the%20restaurant%20in%20Pittsburgh%20in%20late%202020.%20Early%20the%20next%20year%2C%20Walter%20Garner%2C%20now%2044%2C%20became%20her%20manager%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGarner%20began%20sexually%20harassing%20Plaintiff%20almost%20immediately%20after%20they%20began%20working%20together%20on%20the%20same%20shift%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20by%20verbally%20harassing%20the%20minor%20and%20making%20sexual%20innuendoes%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20His%20comments%20%26quot%3Bbecame%20both%20more%20overt%20and%20more%20frequent%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20making%20remarks%20about%20the%20minor's%20butt%20and%20repeatedly%20asking%20to%20see%20her%20outside%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarner%20then%20began%20touching%20her%20inappropriately%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%20When%20she%20asked%20him%20to%20stop%2C%20he%20told%20her%20she%20was%20being%20uptight%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20behaved%20similarly%20toward%20two%20other%20female%20minors%20who%20worked%20at%20the%20restaurant%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20minors%20told%20the%20restaurant's%20hiring%20manager%20about%20the%20harassment%2C%20but%20the%20franchise%20business%20didn't%20take%20any%20action%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20claims.%20The%20minor%20whose%20family%20filed%20the%20lawsuit%20says%20she%20didn't%20receive%20any%20training%20related%20to%20sexual%20harassment%20in%20the%20workplace%20when%20she%20started%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%20February%202021%2C%20the%20minor%20went%20into%20the%20bathroom%20during%20her%20break%20because%20she%20was%20not%20feeling%20well.%20%26quot%3BGarner%20entered%20the%20bathroom%20after%20her%2C%20grabbed%20Plaintiff%20and%20overpowered%20her%2C%20pulled%20off%20her%20McDonald's%20uniform%2C%20and%20raped%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20says%20that%20the%20minor%20went%20%26quot%3Binto%20shock.%26quot%3B%20She%20tried%20to%20forget%20about%20the%20incident%20and%20continued%20working%20at%20the%20restaurant%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20at%20some%20point%20after%20this%2C%20more%20senior%20managers%20at%20the%20restaurant%20saw%20video%20footage%20of%20Garner%20groping%20the%20minor%20while%20they%20were%20investigating%20a%20theft%20from%20the%20cash%20drawer.%20They%20spoke%20to%20Garner%20about%20his%20conduct%20but%20didn't%20discipline%20him%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20Garner%20continued%20to%20harass%20the%20minor%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%20%26quot%3BGarner%20attempted%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20Plaintiff%20inside%20the%20kids'%20area%20at%20the%20McDonald's%20location%20in%20question%2C%20but%20Plaintiff%20refused%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%20%26quot%3BGarner%20pressured%20Plaintiff%20to%20meet%20with%20him%20after%20work%2C%20where%20he%20again%20used%20pressure%20and%20influence%20to%20coerce%20Plaintiff%20into%20sexual%20acts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20Garner%20showed%20some%20photos%20of%20himself%20and%20the%20plaintiff%20to%20another%20minor%20worker%20at%20the%20restaurant%2C%20who%20told%20her%20school%20administration%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20Staff%20at%20the%20school%20called%20the%20police%2C%20who%20started%20an%20investigation%20the%20next%20day%2C%20the%20plaintiff%E2%80%99s%20lawyers%20said.%20Police%20arrested%20Garner%20on%20May%2021%2C%202021%2C%20according%20to%20his%20criminal%20docket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20he%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20offenses%20including%20statutory%20sexual%20assault%20and%20indecent%20assault%20of%20a%20minor%2C%20his%20criminal%20docket%20shows.%20He%20was%20sentenced%20to%20a%20minimum%20of%20four%20years%20in%20prison%2C%20and%20a%20maximum%20of%2010.%20Garner%20remains%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERice%20Enterprises%20only%20fired%20Garner%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20we%20were%20made%20aware%20of%20the%20complaint%20against%20Garner%20in%202021%2C%20we%20terminated%20his%20employment%20and%20offered%20our%20full%20support%20to%20the%20impacted%20employees%20and%20law%20enforcement%20investigating%20this%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rice%20Enterprises%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20BI%20by%20its%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarner%20had%20previously%20spent%20time%20in%20prison%20over%20the%20sexual%20assault%20of%20a%2010-year-old%20in%201999%20and%20was%20registered%20as%20a%20permanent%20sex%20offender%20on%20the%20Megan's%20Law%20sex%20offender%20registry%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit%20and%20documents%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20minor's%20attorneys%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20they%20agreed%20to%20a%20settlement%20so%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20have%20to%20endure%20the%20%26quot%3Badditional%20stress%20and%20trauma%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20statement%2C%20Rice%20Enterprises%20said%20provides%20%E2%80%9Call%20employees%20with%20a%20strict%20policy%20on%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20policies%20and%20procedures%20for%20reporting%20any%20violations.%26quot%3B%20It%20said%20that%20since%20learning%20of%20Garner's%20harassment%2C%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bredoubled%20our%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20a%20positive%20and%20respectful%20experience%20for%20all%20employees%20in%20our%20restaurants%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERice%20Enterprises%20said%20it%20conducts%20background%20checks%20on%20%E2%80%9Call%20management%20positions%E2%80%9D%20and%20put%20Garner's%20hiring%20down%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bthird-party%20vendor%2C%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftriblive.com%2Flocal%2Fbethel-park-mcdonalds-franchise-sued-over-sex-assault-by-ex-manager-settles-with-teen-victim-for-4-35m%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cu%3Enamed%20by%20local%20outlet%20TribLive%20as%20Backgroundchecks.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20it%20said%20reported%20that%20Garner%20did%20not%20have%20any%20previous%20arrests%20or%20issues.%20Rice%20Enterprises%20sued%20the%20vendor%2C%20Backgroundchecks.com%20in%20May%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20lawsuit%20viewed%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20events%20that%20took%20place%20in%20this%20case%20are%20deeply%20troubling%2C%E2%80%9D%20McDonald%E2%80%99s%20USA%20told%20BI.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20working%20under%20the%20Arches%20deserves%20to%20feel%20safe%20and%20respected%20when%20they%20come%20to%20work%2C%20and%20sexual%20harassment%20or%20violence%20of%20any%20kind%20is%20completely%20unacceptable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20committed%20to%20providing%20franchisees%20with%20the%20resources%20they%20need%20to%20create%20a%20safe%20working%20environment%20in%20their%20restaurants%20%E2%80%93%20including%20training%20around%20harassment%20prevention%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%