0have%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20his%20decision%20to%20switch%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESon%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Shankarrao%20Chavan%2C%20Ashok%20Chavan%20wields%20significant%20influence%20in%20the%20Nanded%20region%20and%20this%20switch%20may%20hurt%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls.%20This%20also%20plays%20out%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20tall%20poll%20challenge%20facing%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20--%20comprising%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20camp%20of%20NCP%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%20Chavan%20has%20had%20an%20eventful%20political%20journey%20so%20far.%20Starting%20out%20as%20a%20student%20leader%20during%20his%20college%20days%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20hold%20key%20posts%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20including%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20chief%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee.%20He%20has%20served%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20Nanded%20on%20two%20occasions%20and%20been%20a%20member%20of%20both%20Houses%20of%20the%20state%20legislature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20serving%20as%20state%20minister%2C%20he%20was%20chosen%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20after%20Vilasrao%20Deshmukh%20stepped%20down%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202008%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20Congress%20retained%20him%20on%20the%20top%20post%20after%20the%202009%20state%20polls.%20The%20stint%20was%2C%20however%2C%20short%20as%20Mr%20Chavan%20was%20forced%20to%20step%20down%20amid%20corruption%20allegations%20related%20to%20the%20Adarsh%20Housing%20Society%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthose-who-are-vulnerable-congress-slams-betrayer-ashok-chavan-as-he-quits-party-5042566%5C%22%3EResponding%20to%20Mr%20Chavan's%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20took%20a%20%26quot%3Bwashing%20machine%26quot%3B%20jab%20--%20washin