%20or%20New%20Delhi%20but%20sources%20at%20Adani%2C%20communicating%20off%20the%20record%20as%20they%20are%20not%20authorised%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media%2C%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20last%20week%20that%20the%20export%20had%20indeed%20taken%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20an%20Indian%20conglomerate%20in%20supplying%20drones%20%E2%80%93%20which%20are%20being%20used%20by%20the%20IDF%20for%20attacks%20in%20densely%20populated%20urban%20areas%20in%20Gaza%20%E2%80%93%20appears%20to%20fly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20official%20position%20seeking%20an%20immediate%20cease-fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20the%20sale%20comes%20even%20as%20judges%20on%20the%20Hague%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20on%20Monday%20ordered%20the%20Dutch%20government%20to%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20the%20export%20of%20F-35%20fighter%20jet%20parts%20to%20Israel%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Finternational%2F2024%2F02%2F12%2Ffgn41-netherlands-israel-f35.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Associated%20Press%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cciting%20a%20clear%20risk%20of%20violations%20of%20international%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Elbit%20Systems%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findias-first-pvt-uav-facility-takes-off-at-hyderabad%2Farticleshow%2F67096441.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentered%20into%20a%20joint%20venture%20with%20Adani%20Defence%20and%20Aerospace%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%2049%25%20share%20and%20opened%20a%20%2415-million%20facility%20in%20Hyderabad%20to%20manufacture%20UAVs%20for%20the%20first%20time%20outside%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%20contacted%20the%20Israeli%20defence%20firm%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20simply%20responded%20that%20they%20could%20%E2%80%9Cconfirm%20that%20Elbit%20Systems%20collaborates%20with%20Adani%2C%20which%20is%20a%20supplier%20to%20our%20UAS%20%5BUnmanned%20Aerial%20Systems%5D%20supply%20chain%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20added%20that%20Elbit%20Systems%20%E2%80%9Ccannot%20comment%20on%20the%20details%20of%20specific%20contracts%2C%20including%20identifying%20suppliers%20and%20the%20content%20they%20provide%20to%20different%20customers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EShephard%20Media%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20UAVs%20were%20delivered%20with%20fully%20assembled%20carbon%20composite%20aerostructures%20produced%20at%20the%2050%2C000%20sq.%20ft%20Adani%20facility%20in%20Hyderabad.%20The%20report%20also%20indicated%20that%20Elbit%20provided%20Hermes%20900%20kits%20to%20India%2C%20along%20with%20necessary%20tools%20like%20sensors%20and%20engines%2C%20for%20the%20assembly%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202023%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2FHwI0q%23selection-1077.0-1085.1%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EHindu%3C%2Fi%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20based%20on%20insights%20from%20an%20anonymous%20source%20regarding%20the%20delivery%20timeline%20of%20Hermes%20900%20UAVs%20for%20the%20Indian%20defence%20services%20amidst%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20aerostructure%20of%20Hermes%20900%20had%20already%20been%20manufactured%20in%20Hyderabad.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20equipment%20has%20to%20come%20in%20from%20Israel%2C%20which%20has%20already%20arrived.%20So%20there%20is%20no%20impact%20in%20that%20regard%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fhaaretz-labels%2F2023-02-12%2Fty-article-labels%2F.premium%2Fopening-the-skies-elbit-systems-is-bringing-the-world-of-drones-to-the-civilian-market%2F00000186-44d8-d553-adb6-dedd1c9c0000%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EHaa