the%20incident%20remains%20unverified%20by%20independent%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%20criticism%2C%20even%20from%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20allies%2C%20has%20mounted%20regarding%20the%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20the%20four%20months%20since%20the%20Hamas%20attack.%20According%20to%20United%20Nations%20agencies%2C%20the%20death%20toll%20which%20exceeds%2028%2C000%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146387%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epredominantly%20comprises%20women%20and%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Last%20Thursday%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F02%2F09%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fbiden-israel-gaza.html%5C%22%3Esharpened%20his%20criticism%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20calling%20its%20Gaza%20response%20%E2%80%98over%20the%20top%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20initially%20expressing%20unconditional%20solidarity%20with%20Israel%20following%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20India%20has%20nuanced%20its%20stance%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20New%20Delhi%20had%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3Eabstained%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20resolution%20in%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20calling%20for%20a%20humanitarian%20pause%20in%20October%202023.%20However%2C%20two%20months%20later%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-votes-in-favour-of-unga-resolution-calling-for-immediate-ceasefire-in-gaza%5C%22%3Evoted%20in%20favour%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2FSpeeches-Statements.htm%3Fdtl%2F37521%2Findias%2Bnational%2Bstatement%2Bby%2Beam%2Bdr%2Bs%2Bjaishankar%2Bat%2Bthe%2B19th%2Bnam%2Bsummit%2Bin%2Bkampala%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20position%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20recently%20articulated%20by%20ex