20FCC%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bcan%20convince%20a%20called%20party%20that%20a%20trusted%20person%2C%20or%20someone%20they%20care%20about%20such%20as%20a%20family%20member%2C%20wants%20or%20needs%20them%20to%20take%20some%20action%20that%20they%20would%20not%20otherwise%20take%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20after%20a%20fake%20robocall%20imitating%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20sought%20to%20dissuade%20people%20from%20voting%20for%20him%20in%20New%20Hampshire's%20Democratic%20primary%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20cease-and-desist%20letter%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20company%2C%20and%20a%20criminal%20investigation%20is%20under%20way%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20use%20of%20generative%20AI%20has%20brought%20a%20fresh%20threat%20to%20voter%20suppression%20schemes%20and%20the%20campaign%20season%20with%20the%20heightened%20believability%20of%20fake%20robocalls%2C%26quot%3B%20FCC%20Commissioner%20Geoffrey%20Starks%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%2C%20which%20goes%20into%20effect%20immediately%2C%20allows%20the%20regulator%20to%20fine%20companies%20that%20use%20AI-generated%20voices%20in%20their%20calls%20or%20restrict%20the%20service%20providers%20that%20carry%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707729060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F2d31g3cg_potus-joe-biden_625x300_19_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdeepfakes-artificial-intelligence-joe-biden-us-bans-ai-powered-voice-robocalls-heres-why-5042584%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20has%20banned%20AI-generated%20robocalls%20amid%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20voice%20cloning%20incidents%20that%20has%20scammed%20thousands%20of%20citizens%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdeepfakes-artificial-intelligence-joe-biden-us-bans-ai-powered-voice-robocalls-