ift%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F25131420%2F45220376405_977141d3c5_o.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20group%20of%20over%20a%20hundred%20civil%20society%20members%2C%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20former%20civil%20servants%2C%20media%20professionals%2C%20and%20academics%20convened%20on%20February%2010%20and%2011%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns%20about%20the%20escalating%20shift%20towards%20totalitarianism%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convention%20highlighted%20measures%20to%20tackle%20leading%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20unemployment%2C%20especially%20amongst%20youth%20and%20women%2C%20stem%20the%20tide%20of%20majoritarian%20communalism%2C%20safeguard%20constitutional%20rights%20and%20the%20autonomy%20of%20statutory%20institutions%2C%20strengthen%20the%20federal%20contract%20and%20promote%20equality%20and%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-day%20Democracy%20Convention%202024%20was%20addressed%20by%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20Salman%20Khurshid%20and%20Manish%20Tewari%2C%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20general%20secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%2C%20MP%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20CPI-M%20Kashmir%20leader%20Mohamad%20Yusuf%20Tarigami%2C%20and%20spokesman%20of%20the%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20Suhail%20Bukhari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20proposals%20put%20forth%20by%20the%20Democracy%20Convention%20were%20calls%20to%20review%20the%20new%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%2C%20and%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bills%2C%20which%20allow%20arrest%20on%20mere%20suspicion%20and%20broaden%20the%20definition%20of%20terrorism%20to%20include%20peaceful%20protests%2C%20such%20as%20roadblocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20it%20recommended%20the%20repeal%20of%20draconian%20legislations%20like%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20(PSA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20press%20release%2C%20the%20convention%20urged%20refraining%20from%20deploying%20armed%20forces%20in%20internal%20conflicts%2C%20endorsing%20the%201951%20recommendation%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fin-illustrations-a-brief-history-of-indias-national-security-laws%5C%22%3EPreventive%20Detention%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20(PDA)%20should%20only%20apply%20during%20a%20state%20of%20war%2C%20and%20reaffirming%20bail%20as%20the%20norm%2C%20with%20exceptions%20only%20for%20the%20rarest%20of%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20convention%20demanded%20a%20comprehensive%20overhaul%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%202002%20(PMLA)%2C%20citing%20its%20alleged%20use%20for%20targeting%20critics%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20called%20on%20the%20government%20to%20provide%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Freality-belies-modi-government-implementing-swaminathan-commission-recommendations%5C%22%3Eimplement%20recommendations%20from%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20advocating%20for%20the%20expansion%20of%20MSP%20to%20various%20crops%20to%20ensure%20income%20security%20and%20promote%20crop%20diversification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20key%20proposals%20included%20strict%20adherence%20to%20the%201992%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20with%20the%201947%20cutoff%20date%20and%20the%20enactment%20of%20a%20comprehensive%20domestic%20anti-discrimination%20law%2C%20safeguarding%20citizens%20against%20discrimination%20across%20various%20fields%20and%20repealing%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20of%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReproduced%20below%20is%20the%20full%20text%20of%20the%20press%20release%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocracy%20Convention%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPress%20Release%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2010-11%2C%202024%2C%20over%20a%20hundred%20members%20of%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20former%20civil%20servants%2C%20media%20professionals%20and%20academics%20came%20together%20to%20express%20their%20distress%20at%20the%20increasingly%20totalitarian%20direction%20in%20which%20our%20country%20is%20being%20led.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convention%20highlighted%20measures%20to%20tackle%20leading%20issues%20such%20as%20unemployment%2C%20especially%20amongst%20youth%20and%20women%2C%20stem%20the%20tide%20of%20majoritarian%20communalism%2C%20safeguard%20constitutional%20rights%20and%20the%20autonomy%20of%20statutory%20institutions%2C%20strengthen%20the%20federal%20contract%20and%20promote%20equality%20and%20social%20justice.%20It%20was%20addressed%20by%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20Salman%20Khurshid%20and%20Manish%20Tewari%2C%20CPI-M%20General-Secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%2C%20MP%20Kapil%20Sibal%20CPI-M%20Kashmir%20leader%20Md.%20Yusuf%20Tarigami%2C%20and%20spokesman%20of%20the%20PDP%2C%20Suhail%20Bukhari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20convention%20proposals%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESeek%20a%20review%20of%20the%20new%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20bill%2C%20which%20allow%20arrest%20on%20mere%20suspicion%20and%20expand%20the%20definition%20of%20terrorism%20to%20include%20even%20peaceful%20protests%2C%20eg%20roadblocks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERepeal%20draconian%20legislation%20such%20as%20the%20UAPA%2C%20including%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20PSA.%20Refrain%20from%20deploying%20the%20armed%20forces%20in%20internal%20conflicts.%20Adopt%20the%201951%20recommendation%20that%20the%20PDA%20should%20only%20apply%20during%20a%20state%20of%20war%3B%20re-affirm%20that%20bail%20must%20be%20a%20norm%20(any%20exception%20must%20be%20for%20the%20rarest%20of%20rare%20offences).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESeek%20a%20complete%20overhaul%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%202002%20(PMLA)%20which%20is%20used%20for%20targeting%20critics%20of%20the%20government%20and%20its%20politics.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGive%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20MSP%20and%20implement%20the%20Swaminathan%20commission.%20Expand%20MSP%20to%20a%20range%20of%20crops%20(pulses%2C%20oilseeds%2C%20millets)%20for%20assured%20income%2C%20encouraging%20crop%20diversification%C2%A0and%20procurement%20of%20diverse%20local%20food%20baskets%20for%20PDS%2FMDMS%2FICDS.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStrictly%20adhere%20to%20the%201992%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20with%20the%20cut-off%20date%20of%201947.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEnact%20a%20comprehensive%20domestic%20anti-discrimination%20law%2C%20that%20protects%20citizens%20against%20discrimination%20on%20grounds%20of%20sex%2C%20caste%2C%20religion%2C%20ethnicity%2C%20sexual%20orientation%2C%20disability%2C%20or%20across%20intersections%20of%20these%20identities%2C%C2%A0in%20a%20range%20of%20fields%20including%20employment%2C%20education%2C%20housing%2C%20health%20care.%20Establish%20a%20Diversity%20Commission.%20Repeal%20the%20CAA%202019.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESupport%20independent%20fact-checkers%20and%20build%20a%20collaboration%20between%20them%20and%20media%20houses%3B%20encourage%20close%20cooperation%20between%20them.%20Remove%20access-related%20restrictions%20on%20the%20media%20for%20parliament%20coverage%20and%20the%20reporting%20of%20government%20ministries.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERestore%20the%20autonomy%20of%20the%20ECI%2C%20CBI%2C%20ED%3B%20fully%20staff%20oversight%20institutions%20through%20an%20independent%20appointment%20process%3B%20work%20towards%20creation%20of%20an%20all-India%20judicial%20service.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3ESeek%20e%3C%2Fem%3Enactment%20of%20The%20Political%20Parties%20(Registration%20and%20Regulation%20of%20Affairs)%20Bill%2C%20drafted%20in%202011.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESeek%20repeal%20of%20The%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20Other%20Election%20Commissioners%20(Appointment%2C%20Conditions%20of%20Service%20and%20Term%20of%20Office)%20Act%2C%202023%2C%20and%20replacement%20of%20the%20government%20appointee%20on%20the%20selection%20committee%20with%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20India.%20The%20ECI%20should%20return%20to%20its%20opposition%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStrengthen%20the%20RTI%20regime%20and%20undo%20the%20regressive%20amendments%20made%20to%20the%20RTI%20Act%20in%202019%20and%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAmend%20the%20Lokpal%20and%20Lokayuktas%20Act%20to%20include%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20selection%20committee%3B%20provide%20for%20setting%20up%20of%20Lokayuktas%20in%20states%20with%20the%20same%20framework%20as%20the%20Lokpal%20at%20the%20centre%3B%20vest%20administrative%20control%20of%20the%20anti-corruption%20wing%20of%20the%20CBI%20in%20the%20Lokpal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERoll-back%20regressive%20amendments%20made%20to%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMeasures%20such%20as%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20undermine%20India%E2%80%99s%20federal%20structure.%20Disband%20the%20Ramnath%20Kovind%20committee.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERepeal%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amdt)%20Act%2C%202023.%20Adhere%20to%20Article%203%3A%20no%20alteration%20to%20states%20borders%20without%20consultation%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20people%20through%20their%20elected%20representatives%3B%20immediately%20restore%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20statehood%20and%20hold%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAppoint%20governors%20only%20in%20consultation%20with%20chief%20ministers%20and%20remove%20them%20only%20following%20a%20resolution%20by%20the%20state%20legislature%20(1988%20Sarkaria%20commission%20and%202010%20M.M.%20Punchhi).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReconsider%20The%20Fiscal%20Responsibility%20and%20Budget%20Management%20(FRBM)%20limit.%20Amend%20Article%20293(3)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20to%20remove%20the%20requirement%20of%20Central%20Government%20permission%20to%20borrow.%C2%A0%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%201969%20Rajamannar%20committee%E2%80%99s%20recommendation%20that%20states%20have%20residuary%20fiscal%20powers%20deserves%20reconsideration.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDepute%20a%20fact-finding%20mission%20composed%20of%20parliamentarians%20and%20civil%20society%20representatives%20to%20propose%20peace-building%20mechanisms%20in%20the%20legislature%20and%20to%20the%20Manipur%20administration%2C%20such%20as%20a%20halt%20to%20violence%2C%20initiation%20of%20dialogue%2C%20control%20over%20the%20proliferation%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOppose%20the%20fencing%20of%20the%20border%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20which%20is%20extremely%20unpopular%20in%20bordering%20states%20such%20as%20Mizoram.%20Consult%20with%20the%20chief%20ministers%20of%20the%20north-eastern%20states%2C%20as%20suggested%20by%20the%20Nagaland%20CM.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReview%20all%20changes%20in%20textbooks%20and%20curriculum%20introduced%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20and%20removing%20anything%20introduced%20which%20is%20not%20supported%20by%20evidence%20or%20argument.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPromote%20cultural%20activities%20that%20encourage%20fraternity%20between%20religious%20and%20language-based%20communities.%20(eg%20Ganga-Jamuna%20Tehzeeb%2C%20the%20commonality%20of%20several%20Indian%20languages%2C%20etc.).%20Revive%20the%20Sahitya%20Akademi%E2%80%99s%20principle%20of%20encouraging%20regional%20and%20local%20language%20literature%20and%20exchange.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConduct%20State-wide%20surveys%20of%20DNTs%2C%20NTs%20and%20SNTs%3B%20Create%20skilling%20and%20re-skilling%20programs%20for%20DNT%20youth%3B%20Accept%20and%20implement%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%202008%20Renake%20Commission.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInclude%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%201989%20and%20its%20amendment%20in%202015%20in%20the%20Ninth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%3B%20establish%20mandatory%20exclusive%20special%20courts%20under%20section%2014%20of%20the%20SCST%20(PoA)%20and%20implement%20rule%204(5)%20to%20appoint%20public%20prosecutors%20of%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20choice.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EImplement%20community%20forest%20rights%20under%20The%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20other%20traditional%20forest%20dwellers%20(Recognition%20of%20Forest%20Rights)%20Act%2C%202006.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERepeal%20the%202023%20amendment%20of%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act%2C%20which%20threatens%20to%20be%20the%20most%20destructive%20of%20all%20the%20decisions%20made%20regarding%20forests%20and%20the%20environment%20so%20far.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EImprove%2C%20expand%20and%20strengthen%20the%20MNREGA.%20Increase%20wages%20to%20Rs%20500%20per%20day%3B%20revoke%20the%20Aadhaar-based%20Mandatory%20Payment%20System%3B%20ensure%20timely%20payment%20of%20wages%20and%20transfer%20of%20funds%20from%20the%20centre%20to%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECreate%20an%20Urban%20Employment%20Guarantee%2C%20specifically%20for%20women%20workers.%20Provide%20policy%20packages%20specifically%20tailored%20to%20MSMEs%20with%20special%20incentives%20for%20employment%20of%20youth.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEnact%20a%20Comprehensive%20Law%20for%20informal%20workers%2C%20extending%20core%20labour%20standards%20to%20all%20segments%20of%20working%20people.%20Ensure%20tripartite%20agreements%20with%20aggregators%2C%20government%20and%20workers%20to%20ensure%20social%20security%20and%20basic%20working%20conditions%20of%20gig%20workers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EProvide%20a%20Life-Cycle%20Social%20Protection%20Floor%20(Sampoorn%20Samajik%20Suraksha)%20that%20gives%20universal%20access%20to%20social%20protection%20(with%20minimal%20exclusion%20criteria).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELegislate%20a%20public%20health%20bill%20making%20health%20a%20human%20right%20and%20incorporating%20safeguards%20against%20discrimination%20and%20denial%20of%20care%20on%20account%20of%20caste%2C%20gender%2C%20ailments%20like%20HIV%2C%20sexual%20preferences%20(MSM%20and%20LGBT)%20or%20lifestyle%20choices%20(sex%20workers).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReverse%20the%20decision%20to%20clear%20hundreds%20of%20hectares%20of%20forest%20in%20the%20pristine%20island%20of%20Great%20Nicobar%20to%20build%20a%20container%20terminal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEnd%20indiscriminate%20construction%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20fragile%20Himalayas.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConvenor%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESd%2F%20Radha%20Kumar%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707720299000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F25131420%2F45220376405_977141d3c5_o.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fover-100-defenders-of-civil-liberties-human-rights-raise-concerns-over-totalitarian-shift-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20convention%20was%20addressed%20by%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20Salman%20Khurshid%20and%20Manish%20Tewari%2C%20CPI(M)%20general%20secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20and%20MP%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20among%20others.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fover-100-defenders-of-civil-liberties-human-rights-raise-concerns-over-totalitarian-shift-in-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20than%2050%20people%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20strikes%20on%20Rafah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707717850000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107618090%2Cimgsize-1339009.cms%22%2C%22origin