2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12112825%2FUntitled-design-8-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Complicated%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98entangled%E2%80%99%20and%20capable%20of%20inviting%20serious%20concern%20for%20the%20sanctity%20of%20its%20democracy%20is%20how%20Urdu%20media%20described%20the%20recent%20elections%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVarious%20political%20analyses%20and%20editorials%20across%20Urdu%20outlets%20expressed%20deep%20worry%20over%20the%20fairness%20of%20the%20polls%20and%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20results%2C%20while%20also%20raising%20questions%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20Election%20Commission%20and%20its%20role.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20focus%20is%20a%20possible%20case%20of%20rigging.%20Were%20the%20votes%20won%20by%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20leader%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20and%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)-supported%20candidate%20Dr.%20Yasmin%20Rashid%20fudged%2C%20asked%20newspapers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20major%20question%20raised%20by%20Urdu%20media%20was%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20independent%20candidates%20backed%20by%20the%20PTI.%20Will%20they%20be%20given%20the%20right%20to%20represent%20their%20constituencies%20or%20will%20there%20be%20some%20measure%20of%20horse-trading%3F%20Will%20manipulative%20politics%20take%20over%20and%20will%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20be%20compromised%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20analysts%20believe%20that%20it%20will%20not%20be%20easy%20for%20anyone%20to%20get%20the%20PTI-backed%20independent%20candidates%20on%20board%20to%20form%20the%20government%20as%20their%20immediate%20demand%20would%20be%20the%20release%20of%20their%20leader%2C%20Imran%20Khan.%20A%20possibility%20has%20also%20been%20expressed%20that%20these%20winning%20candidates%20will%20never%20stop%20milking%20public%20sympathy%20for%20Imran%20Khan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20some%20analyses%2C%20the%20poll%20outcome%20has%20been%20linked%20directly%20to%20the%20popularity%20of%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20who%20is%20in%20jail%20and%20facing%20many%20charges.%20It%20is%20claimed%20that%20he%20put%20up%20a%20strong%20and%20successful%20political%20fight%20against%20the%20establishment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20while%20many%20serious%20questions%20have%20been%20raised%20on%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20elections%20due%20to%20the%20delay%20and%20sluggishness%20in%20the%20announcement%20of%20results%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20security%20agencies%20are%2C%20at%20once%2C%20being%20lauded%20for%20conducting%20peaceful%20polls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20some%20analysts%20have%20referred%20to%20the%20new%20political%20situation%20in%20Pakistan%20as%20an%20%E2%80%98after%20shock%E2%80%99.%20To%20overcome%20the%20devastation%20caused%20by%20it%20will%20not%20be%20easy%2C%20they%20have%20claimed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.express.com.pk%2Fepaper%2FPoPupwindow.aspx%3FnewsID%3D1110796894%26Issue%3DNP_KHI%26Date%3D20240211%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20Urdu%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20coalition%20government%E2%80%99s%20task%20ahead%20is%20riddled%20with%20challenges.%20The%20biggest%20one%2C%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20government%2C%20will%20be%20to%20ensure%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20stability.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FGEOHeJZzp2A%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Have%20the%20Pakistan%20Elections%20Made%20the%20Country%E2%80%99s%20Crisis%20Worse%3F%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuestions%20on%20autonomy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOut%20of%20the%20many%20analyses%20and%20editorials%20of%20the%20previous%20two%20days%20in%20Urdu%20media%2C%20two%20pertinent%20questions%20have%20been%20raised%20by%20eminent%20litterateur%20Zahida%20Hina.%20Will%20the%20autonomy%20of%20the%20National%20Assembly%20that%20will%20come%20into%20existence%20as%20a%20result%20of%20these%20elections%20be%20accepted%3F%20Will%20the%20prime%20minister%20elected%20by%20the%20parliament%20be%20able%20to%20complete%20his%20constitutional%20term%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20future%20of%20Pakistan%20depends%20on%20the%20answers%20to%20these%20two%20questions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20let%20us%20look%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.jang.com.pk%2Fkarachi%2F11-02-2024%2Fpage7%5C%22%3EUrdu%20daily%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.jang.com.pk%2Fkarachi%2F11-02-2024%2Fpage7%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJang%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.jang.com.pk%2Fkarachi%2F11-02-2024%2Fpage7%5C%22%3E%20which%20has%20termed%20the%20recently%20held%20polls%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20biggest%20elections%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20country.%20In%20one%20of%20its%20editorials%2C%20it%20said%20that%20these%20elections%20were%20held%20at%20a%20time%20when%20terrorism%20is%20once%20again%20raising%20its%20head%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20view%20of%20the%20perceived%20terror%20threat%2C%20postponement%20of%20the%20elections%20was%20also%20speculated%20but%20with%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20security%20agencies%2C%20voting%20was%20conducted%20peacefully%20across%20the%20country%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDescribing%20the%20last%20five%20years%20of%20Pakistan%20as%20a%20phase%20that%20saw%20the%20worst%20political%20crisis%2C%20the%20editorial%20said%20that%20these%20years%20have%20had%20a%20deep%20impact%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economy%2C%20resulting%20in%20severe%20inflation.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20people%20took%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20these%20elections%20and%20the%20process%20also%20carried%20with%20it%20a%20sense%20of%20hope%2C%20it%20claimed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20column%20further%20stated%20that%20since%20no%20party%20got%20a%20majority%2C%20the%20role%20of%20independent%20candidates%20in%20the%20House%20has%20become%20crucial.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20urged%20all%20political%20parties%20to%20work%20together%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpolitics-bounces-back-in-pakistan%5C%22%3EPolitics%20Bounces%20Back%20in%20Pakistan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20strong%20government%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.jang.com.pk%2Fkarachi%2F11-02-2024%2Fpage7%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJang%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.jang.com.pk%2Fkarachi%2F11-02-2024%2Fpage7%5C%22%3E%20also%20emphasised%20separately%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20political%20leadership%20will%20have%20to%20take%20decisions%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20nation%2C%20beyond%20personal%20and%20party%20interests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20of%20the%20newspaper%E2%80%99s%20analyses%20refer%20to%20electoral%20transparency%20and%20say%20that%20its%20biggest%20proof%20is%20that%20opposition%20candidates%20have%20received%20good%20votes%20in%20PML-N%E2%80%99s%20stronghold%20Lahore.%20It%20has%20clarified%20that%20not%20all%20independent%20winners%20are%20PTI%20supported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20negative%20aspect%20of%20these%20results%20has%20also%20been%20highlighted.%20It%20is%20feared%20that%20since%20no%20party%20got%20the%20majority%2C%20a%20strong%20and%20powerful%20democratic%20government%20will%20not%20be%20formed.%20Such%20a%20government%20is%20crucial%20to%20handle%20political%20instability%20and%20save%20the%20sinking%20economy%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20analysis%20claimed%20that%20Imran%20Khan%20was%20unfairly%20targeted%20and%20thrown%20behind%20bars.%20Had%20the%20elections%20been%20transparent%2C%20Imran%20would%20have%20won%20with%20a%20clear%20majority%2C%20it%20said.%20The%20analyst%20quoted%20the%20international%20media%20and%20claimed%20that%20seven%20out%20of%20ten%20Pakistanis%20do%20not%20have%20confidence%20in%20the%20transparency%20of%20elections.%20It%20added%20that%20it%20was%20like%20a%20puppet%20show%20which%20will%20continue%20because%20what%20happened%20cannot%20be%20termed%20rigging%20but%20a%20dacoity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20some%20analysts%20believe%20that%20the%20people%20defeated%20both%20capitalistic%20and%20tyrannical%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerrorism%2C%20law%20and%20order%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.express.com.pk%2Fepaper%2FPoPupwindow.aspx%3FnewsID%3D1110795113%26Issue%3DNP_KHI%26Date%3D20240210%23google_vignette%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDaily%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EExpress%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.express.com.pk%2Fepaper%2FPoPupwindow.aspx%3FnewsID%3D1110795113%26Issue%3DNP_KHI%26Date%3D20240210%23google_vignette%5C%22%3E%20has%20not%20given%20any%20direct%20opinion%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20elections%20and%20its%20results.%20However%2C%20it%20claimed%20that%20the%20holding%20of%20elections%20has%20restored%20people%E2%80%99s%20trust%20in%20democracy.%20One%20of%20its%20editorials%20said%20that%20in%20the%20current%20situation%20the%20party%20that%20forms%20the%20government%20should%20first%20improve%20law%20and%20order%20because%20without%20crushing%20terrorism%20the%20dream%20of%20economic%20development%20will%20not%20be%20fulfilled.%20Emphasising%20the%20need%20for%20a%20stable%20government%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EExpress%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20wished%20for%20a%20government%20that%20provides%20employment%20and%20controls%20inflation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20analyses%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EDaily%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20praised%20the%20Pakistani%20Army%20for%20being%20the%20pride%20of%20the%20country%20as%20it%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20conducting%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20some%20concerns%20for%20the%20new%20government%20and%20it%20is%20claimed%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20rough%20for%20the%20new%20parliament%20and%20the%20government.%20Everyone%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20gravity%20of%20economic%20crises%20in%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20threat%20of%20terrorism%20is%20also%20lurking.%20It%20is%20very%20important%20to%20arrest%20the%20group%20with%20many%20faces%20which%20is%20active%20inside%20Pakistan%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20paper%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%20also%20advocated%20for%20carrying%20forward%20the%20democratic%20process%20in%20the%20country%20smoothly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-election-no-matter-who-wins-the-army-will-rule-the-roost%5C%22%3EPakistan%20Election%3A%20No%20Matter%20Who%20Wins%2C%20the%20Army%20Will%20Rule%20the%20Roost%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHorse%20trading%20and%20manipulation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20same%20way%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.dunya.com.pk%2Findex.php%3Fe_name%3DLHR%26edate%3D2024-02-10%26page%3D25%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.dunya.com.pk%2Findex.php%3Fe_name%3DLHR%26edate%3D2024-02-10%26page%3D25%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDaily%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDuniya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.dunya.com.pk%2Findex.php%3Fe_name%3DLHR%26edate%3D2024-02-10%26page%3D25%5C%22%3E%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20most%20of%20the%20independent%20candidates%20have%20won%20and%20a%20coalition%20government%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20the%20making.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20quoted%20Nawaz%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20offer%20to%20all%20the%20parties%20to%20form%20a%20government%20together.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20Pakistan%20belongs%20to%20all%20of%20us.%20Everyone%20should%20come%20together%20to%20get%20the%20country%20out%20of%20its%20difficulties.%20People%E2%80%99s%20aspirations%20should%20be%20fulfilled.%20Only%20then%20will%20we%20come%20out%20of%20this%20maelstrom%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPraising%20the%20former%20PM%E2%80%99s%20offer%2C%20the%20newspaper%20commented%20that%20although%20the%20offer%20is%20good%20and%20political%20parties%20should%20work%20together%2C%20if%20a%20new%20market%20of%20manipulation%20and%20trading%20the%20support%20of%20elected%20members%20is%20opened%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20achieving%20parliamentary%20supremacy%2C%20it%20will%20be%20nothing%20more%20than%20the%20theft%20of%20the%20mandate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20added%20that%20if%20the%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20(N)%20is%20able%20to%20form%20the%20government%20with%20the%20Pakistan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20and%20other%20parties%2C%20another%20chapter%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Democratic%20Movement%20government%20will%20be%20witnessed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20this%20political%20alliance%20may%20have%20ruled%20the%20country%20for%20about%2016%20months%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20its%20performance%20was%20nothing%20to%20write%20home%20about.%20Be%20it%20inflation%20or%20unemployment%2C%20the%20country%20rose%20on%20every%20negative%20index.%20Political%20tension%20and%20instability%20also%20remained%20at%20their%20peak%20during%20this%20phase.%20Even%20after%20the%20government%20collapsed%2C%20the%20coalition%20parties%20kept%20blaming%20each%20other%20for%20inflation%20and%20economic%20decline%20and%20no%20party%20readily%20took%20responsibility%20for%20the%20decisions%20of%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%20added%20that%20the%20changing%20trends%20among%20voters%20should%20worry%20politicians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20put%20the%20Election%20Commission%20in%20the%20dock%20due%20to%20the%20delay%20in%20declaring%20the%20election%20results.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20a%20government%20be%20formed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Duniya%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20analyses%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20instability%20of%20the%20incoming%20government%20and%20claimed%20that%20if%20Imran%20Khan%20commands%20a%20strong%20hold%20on%20the%20independent%20members%2C%20they%20will%20not%20join%20the%20government.%20Instead%20they%20would%20demand%20that%20the%20charges%20on%20their%20leader%20should%20be%20dropped.%20They%20can%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20government%20only%20if%20the%20new%20government%20accepts%20their%20demand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20is%20widely%20believed%20that%20this%20matter%20will%20create%20hindrances%20in%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20government.%20If%20the%20independent%20members%20choose%20N%20(League)%2C%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20will%20remain%20in%20the%20opposition.%20However%2C%20in%20this%20situation%20the%20original%20PTI%20will%20not%20be%20part%20of%20this%20stratagem%20and%20there%20will%20be%20a%20risk%20of%20an%20unstable%20government.%20Imran%20Khan%20is%20a%20rebel%20by%20nature.%20He%20is%20bound%20to%20resist%20and%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20new%20government%20will%20continue%20to%20hang%20in%20the%20balance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20analysis%20also%20states%20that%20these%20results%20once%20again%20prove%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20in%20store%20for%20religious%20groups%20in%20electoral%20politics.%20It%20has%20given%20the%20credit%20of%20peaceful%20elections%20to%20Pakistan%20Army.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nawaiwaqt.com.pk%2F10-Feb-2024%2F1764367%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20daily%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENawa-e-Waqt%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nawaiwaqt.com.pk%2F10-Feb-2024%2F1764367%5C%22%3E%20has%20also%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20transparency%20of%20the%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20wrote%20that%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20political%20instability%20currently%20being%20created%20in%20the%20country%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20polls%20is%20also%20posing%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20security%20and%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20of%20the%20country.%20Therefore%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20all%20stakeholders%20including%20the%20political%20leadership%20to%20come%20together%20and%20decide%20on%20a%20concrete%20strategy%20to%20stabilise%20the%20elected%20assembly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20some%20of%20its%20analyses%2C%20the%20election%20results%20have%20been%20described%20as%20sympathy%20for%20Imran%20Khan%20and%20public%20anger.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%20also%20jibed%20at%20the%20current%20results%20and%20the%20discrepancies%20in%20them%20saying%20that%20it%20seemed%20to%20be%20the%20work%20of%20%E2%80%98secret%20angels%E2%80%99%20who%20cast%20their%20votes.%20These%20%E2%80%98angels%E2%80%99%20also%20took%20away%20votes%2C%20when%20convenient%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20democratic%20protocol%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDaily%20Ausaf%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20questioned%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20wrote%20that%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20accept%20their%20respective%20situations%20instead%20of%20forming%20a%20government%20through%20horse%20trading.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20its%20analyses%20stated%20that%20these%20results%20will%20perhaps%20open%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20establishment.%20It%20espoused%20a%20democratic%20way%20and%20discouraged%20the%20buying%20out%20of%20independent%20candidates.%20If%20this%20happens%2C%20it%20will%20be%20no%20less%20than%20a%20political%20revolution.%20With%20this%2C%20the%20previous%20blot%20of%20interference%20in%20politics%20by%20the%20establishment%2C%20that%20is%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20Army%20will%20be%20cleaned%20and%20democracy%20will%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20flourish%2C%20the%20paper%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAusaf%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailyausaf.com%2Fepaper%2Fpage%3Fstation_id%3D2%26page_id%3D201990%26date%3D2024-02-11%5C%22%3Eobserved%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20is%20important%20for%20political%20parties%20to%20keep%20the%20democratic%20protocol%20in%20mind%20and%20heartily%20congratulate%20each%20other%20on%20their%20victory.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20has%20strongly%20advocated%20for%20all%20parties%20to%20come%20together%20to%20form%20the%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawnnews.tv%2Fnews%2F1224379%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDawn%20Urdu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawnnews.tv%2Fnews%2F1224379%5C%22%3E%20has%20written%20in%20its%20editorial%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20history%20will%20testify%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20failed%20to%20fulfil%20all%20its%20responsibilities%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDawn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20also%20held%20the%20incumbent%20government%20and%20the%20entire%20state%20machinery%20responsible%20for%20it%20and%20has%20written%20that%20it%20has%20already%20become%20clear%20that%20these%20elections%20will%20not%20prove%20to%20be%20the%20solution%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20political%20crisis.%20Using%20fear%20tactics%20to%20suppress%20dissent%20will%20likely%20lead%20the%20country%20to%20crisis%20and%20instability.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20shame%20that%20such%20an%20important%20opportunity%20was%20carelessly%20wasted%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20short%2C%20Urdu%20media%20has%20expressed%20various%20concerns%20over%20the%20results%20and%20has%20also%20expressed%20the%20apprehension%20that%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20PTI%20may%20not%20keep%20quiet%20and%20will%20likely%20come%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20in%20protest%20before%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20next%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Hindi%20original%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707717691000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12112825%2FUntitled-design-8-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Furdu-media-pakistan-imran-khan-independents-nawaz-sharif%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20Urdu%20media%2C%20the%20coalition%20government%E2%80%99s%20task%20ahead%20is%20riddled%20with%20challenges.%20The%20biggest%20one%2C%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20government%2C%20will%20be%20to%20ensure%20the%20government's%20stability.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Furdu-media-pakistan-imran-khan-independents-nawaz-sharif%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Signature%20Global%20to%20develop%20housing%20project%20in%20Gurugram%20as%20demand%20surges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707717656000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3