I%20activist.%20The%20letter%20also%20includes%20an%20image%20of%20a%20cheetah%20cub%20being%20treated%2C%20its%20right%20foot%20in%20a%20cast.%20The%20MP-based%20activist%E2%80%99s%20posts%20claim%20that%20authorities%20%E2%80%98hid%E2%80%99%20this%20development.%20However%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20management%20of%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20have%20rejected%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20contacted%20officials%20in%20the%20Forest%20Department%20for%20an%20official%20response%20regarding%20this.%20The%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20once%20they%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECub%20fractured%20foot%2C%20was%20treated%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh-based%20RTI%20activist%20Ajay%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20posts%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%3Ffbid%3D7972895612726175%26set%3Da.896022567080217%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAjaydubey9%2Fstatus%2F1755795520218652770%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3ETwitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20(both%20dated%20February%209)%20called%20for%20an%20investigation%20into%20how%20and%20when%20a%20cheetah%20cub%20kept%20in%20a%20closed%20enclosure%20in%20Kuno%20suffered%20from%20a%20foot%20fracture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubey%2C%20in%20his%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20has%20uploaded%20photographs%20of%20an%20official%20correspondence%20dated%20December%205%20from%20the%20Chief%20Conservator%20of%20Forests%20and%20Director%20of%20the%20Lion%20Project%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Sharma%2C%20in%20reply%20to%20an%20inquiry%20from%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority.%20The%20letter%20from%20Sharma%20details%20that%20a%20then%20eight-month-old%20African%20cheetah%20cub%20was%20injured%20on%20November%2028%20last%20year.%20Veterinarians%20treated%20the%20cub%20the%20next%20day%20for%20a%20fracture%20of%20its%20right%20foot.%3C%