2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F37587%2FTranscript%2Bof%2BWeekly%2BMedia%2BBriefing%2Bby%2Bthe%2BOfficial%2BSpokesperson%2BFebruary%2B08%2B2024%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20last%20weekly%20media%20briefing%20on%20February%208%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson%20had%20said%20that%20they%20were%20still%20looking%20at%20whether%20to%20lodge%20an%20appeal%20against%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20turning%20the%20death%20sentence%20into%20multiple%20prison%20sentences.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Qatar%20situation%2C%20the%20situation%20as%20far%20as%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20remains%20the%20same%20as%20what%20I%20had%20informed%20you%20earlier.%20There%20is%20a%2060-day%20window%20within%20which%20this%20process%20of%20appeal%20has%20to%20be%20filed.%20So%20that%20is%20where%20we%20are.%20The%20situation%20has%20not%20changed.%20We%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20family%20members.%20We%20are%20also%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20legal%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson%20had%20said%20four%20days%20ago.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fqatar-8-navy-veterans-hubris-india-diplomacy%5C%22%3ESaving%20the%20Qatar%208%3A%20Did%20Hubris%20Hurt%20India%E2%80%99s%20Diplomacy%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20eight%20naval%20veterans%2C%20who%20had%20been%20detained%20since%20August%202022%2C%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fqatar-eight-former-indian-navy-officers-handed-death-penalty%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esentenced%20to%20death%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20Court%20of%20First%20Instance%20on%20October%2026%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20termed%20itself%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20shocked%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20verdict%2C%20but%20had%20refrained%20from%20any%20criticism.%20Even%20when%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20a%20small%20t%C3%AAte-%C3%A0-t%C3%AAte%20with%20Qatar%20at%20the%20COP%20summit%20in%20Dubai%20in%20December%2C%20India%20never%20explicitly%20mentioned%20whether%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20eight%20naval%20veterans%20was%20brought%20up.%20Modi%20later%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1730879676875481375%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eposted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20they%20had%20discussed%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpotential%20of%20bilateral%20partnership%20and%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20Qatar%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20freed%20men%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faninews.in%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fwouldnt-have-been-possible-freed-navy-vets-chant-bharat-mata-ki-jai-praise-pm-modi-on-return-from-qatar20240212064803%2F%5C%22%3Espoke%20to%20the%20news%20agency%20ANI%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20it%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20were%20it%20not%20for%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWorking%20for%20the%20now-defunct%20Omani%20private%20company%20Dahra%20Global%20Technologies%20and%20Consultancy%20Services%2C%20they%20were%20engaged%20to%20deliver%20training%20and%20related%20services%20to%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20armed%20forces.%20Although%20the%20specific%20charges%20have%20never%20been%20disclosed%2C%20media%20reports%20suggested%20the%20possibility%20of%20espionage%20allegations%20against%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20November%2C%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fqatar-court-accepts-appeal-application-against-death-sentence-to-8-indian-navy-veterans%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccepted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20application%20against%20the%2