-Sachdeva-5-1707395429-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341176%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20principal%20grievance%20of%20the%20women%20officers%20was%20that%20by%20denying%20them%20a%20permanent%20commission%2C%20they%20were%20subjected%20to%20gender%20discrimination.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Kargil%20war%20veteran%20(who%20prefers%20to%20remain%20anonymous)%20who%20joined%20the%20armed%20forces%20in%201996%2C%20says%20she%20was%20%E2%80%98released%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20service%20after%20a%20total%20of%2012%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20her%20experience%20in%20the%20IAF%2C%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20underwent%20the%20exact%20same%20training%20of%20one%20year%20along%20with%20male%20cadets.%20We%20never%20took%20help%20from%20anyone%20in%20doing%20our%20duty%20or%20task%2C%20be%20it%20night%20guard%20patrol%20check%20duty%20or%20any%20other%20professional%20task.%20My%20trainer%20said%20no%20one%20should%20be%20able%20to%20say%20that%20we%20were%20less%20than%20any%20male%20counterpart.%20And%20I%20ensured%20that%20no%20one%20could%20point%20out%20anything%20just%20because%20I%20am%20a%20female.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20individual%20officers%20are%20good%20but%20female%20officers%20in%20general%20were%20treated%20like%20guinea%20pigs%20%E2%80%93%20experimented%20on%20and%20then%20thrown%20away.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20IAF%20and%20serve%20for%20more%20years%2C%20just%20like%20my%20male%20counterparts%2C%20but%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20