vaan-cover-1707372948.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%2015-year-old%20Nirvaan%20started%20Project%20Jeans%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FNirvaan-cover-1707372948.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FNirvaan-cover-1707372948-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FNirvaan-cover-1707372948-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FNirvaan-cover-1707372948-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FNirvaan-cover-1707372948-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341125%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202022%2C%2017-year-old%20Nirvaan%20started%20Project%20Jeans%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20happened%20during%20the%20winter%20season%2C%20as%20the%20Delhi%20resident%20observed%20his%20family%20donating%20blankets%20to%20the%20underprivileged%20on%20the%20streets.%20Nirvaan%20recognised%20that%20blankets%20offered%20only%20a%20short-term%20solution%20and%20might%20not%20endure%20the%20harsh%20winters%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20kill%20two%20birds%20with%20one%20stone%3A%20repurposing%20old%20denim%20to%20create%20sleeping%20bags.%20This%20initiative%20not%20only%20prevented%20jeans%20from%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills%20but%20also%20offered%20a%20durable%20and%20warm%20sleeping%20option%20for%20the%20homeless%20during%20freezing%20winters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%202022%2C%20%E2%80%98Project%20Jeans%20%E2%80%94%20Blue%20To%20Green%E2%80%99%20has%20distributed%20over%202%2C000%20sleeping%20bags%20across%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Himachal%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20even%20Turkey%20and%20Syria%20by%20recycl