edom.%20It%20feels%20meditative%20and%20makes%20me%20feel%20independent.%20Travelling%20gives%20me%20a%20different%20perspective%20on%20life.%20I%20also%20started%20challenging%20my%20limitations%20by%20trekking.%20Every%20trek%20feels%20like%20an%20attempt%20to%20conquer%20our%20physical%20and%20mental%20obstacles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoushmi%20had%20support%20from%20her%20in-laws%20as%20she%20embarked%20on%20these%20trips.%20Her%20children%2C%20too%2C%20learnt%20to%20be%20independent.%20Vedansh%20also%20started%20attending%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20helped%20me%20give%20my%20kids%20direction%20and%20motivate%20them.%20Both%20my%20kids%20are%20not%20dependent%20on%20me%20now.%20Vedansh%20takes%20care%20of%20himself%20with%20his%20limitations%20and%20capabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20one%20night%20biking%20trips%2C%20Moushmi%20decided%20that%20it%20was%20time%20to%20go%20on%20her%20dream%C2%A0ride%20to%20Ladakh.%20Initially%2C%20she%20admits%20to%20being%20scared%20as%20she%20was%20a%20new%20rider%20and%20this%20would%20be%20her%20first%20long%20distance%20trip.%20But%20having%20crossed%20the%20age%20of%2035%20at%20that%20time%2C%20she%20decided%20that%20it%20was%20now%20or%20never.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20have%20a%20worry%20at%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20something%20were%20to%20happen%20to%20me.%20What%20would%20happen%20if%20the%20decision%20I%20took%20was%20the%20wrong%20one%3F%20People%20cautioned%20me%20against%20it%2C%20saying%20what%20if%20something%20happens%20to%20you%20on%20the%20trip%3F%20But%20I%20had%20decided%20that%20the%20trip%20was%20mandatory%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20her%20sons%20were%20very%20supportive%20of%20her%20decision%20and%20the%20reason%20she%20could%20take%20this%20decision%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20could%20manage%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20first%20long%20biking%20trip%2C%C2%A0%20she%20went%20to%20Leh%20Ladakh%20for%2010%20days.%20She%20recounts%20that%20it%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%20but%20both%20mother%20and%20son%20learnt%20to%20manage%20without%20one%20other%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20a%20shiver%20would%20run%20down%20my%20spine%20whenever%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20home.%20I%20would%20worry%20if%20Vedansh%20was%20doing%20okay.%20It%20was%20difficult%20for%20both%20of%20us.%20But%20after%20overcoming%20the%20initial%20hiccups%2C%20he%20adjusted%20very%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20away%20from%20each%20other%20for%20such%20a%20long%20time%20was%20a%20first%20for%20both%20mother%20and%20son.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20all%20hunky%20dory%2C%20adds%20the%20mother.%20There%20were%20teething%20troubles%20initially%2C%20but%20they%20both%20got%20used%20to%20it%20over%20time%2C%20and%20when%20Moushmi%20came%20back%20with%20a%20certificate%20for%20completing%20the%20trip%2C%20Vedansh%20was%20very%20happy%20and%20proud%20of%20his%20%E2%80%98mumma%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Vedansh%20got%20the%20travel%20bug%20from%20his%20mother.%20He%2C%20too%2C%20has%20explored%20many%20countries%20and%20celebrated%20his%2019th%20birthday%20at%20Jungfrau%2C%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20points%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxQjUs3yB1b%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxQjUs3yB1b%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20pos