20washrooms.%20The%20prices%20range%20between%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%203%2C000%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20season.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20private%20rooms%20with%20a%20shared%20washroom.%20The%20prices%20range%20from%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%202%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfsana%20also%20has%20a%20room%20perfect%20for%20backpackers%20and%20travellers%20on%20a%20budget.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20shared%20rooms%20provide%20an%20economical%20option%20at%20600%20rupees%20per%20bed.%20Washrooms%20are%20shared%20among%20guests%20in%20this%20category%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20experiences%20she%20provides%20in%20her%20homestay%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20provide%20a%20purely%20simple%20Himachali%20food%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337937%2Fbest-budget-homestay-in-uttarakhand-the-nanda-stone-mukteshwar-by-ashish-verma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperience%20at%20our%20homestay.%20%3C%2Fa%3EOur%20caretaker%20and%20old%20cook%20from%20back%20home%20joined%20me%20with%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20homestay%20and%20cooked%20these%20delicious%20meals.%20We%20use%20our%20mother%E2%80%99s%20recipes%20for%20making%20the%20traditional%20dish%2C%20%3Cem%3ESiddu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20served%20to%20our%20guests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20raw%20materials%20are%20usually%20sourced%20from%20her%20home%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20walnuts%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Esiddu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20ghee%20for%20the%20food%2C%20the%20veggies%20and%20milk%20are%20all%20sourced%20from%20my%20own%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-5-1707226745.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20offers%20