orporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20at%20L%26amp%3BT%2C%20explained%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20focus%20on%20STEM%20was%20made%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%20has%20undertaken%20a%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20facilitate%20access%20to%20STEM%20education%20in%20government%20schools%20and%20schools%20with%20limited%20resources.%20This%20initiative%20is%20designed%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20and%20ensure%20that%20students%20have%20the%20necessary%20tools%20and%20opportunities%20to%20develop%20skills%20essential%20for%20the%20evolving%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20different%20models%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20STEM%20education%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302015%2Fboson-whitewater-bengaluru-startup-converts-stp-water-to-high-quality-potable-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20science%20labs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20implementing%20digital%20classrooms%2C%20and%20providing%20DIY%20kits%2C%20among%20other%20approaches.%20We%20did%20not%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20just%20one%20model%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20we%20decided%20on%20a%20blended%20approach%2C%20working%20to%20address%20the%20specific%20needs%20of%20each%20school%20as%20cracking%20just%20one%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle%20is%20not%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mabel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmbracing%20the%20Smart%20School%20concept%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20initially%20focussed%20on%20furnishing%20schools%20with%20fundamental%20infrastructure%20before%20progressing%20to%20the%20establishment%20of%20STEM%20labs.%20However%2C%20their%20original%20plan%20underwent%20adjustments%20due%20to%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic%20coinciding%20with%20the%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommencing%20with%2065%20schools%20nationwide%2C%20it%20pivoted%20to%20online%20classes%20and%20modules%20in%20response%20to%20the%20cha