ine%20science%20fair%20to%20showcase%20their%20creations.%20We%20were%20amazed%20by%20the%20projects%20they%20came%20up%20with%3B%20it%20fired%20their%20creativity%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Mabel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%20collaborates%20with%20local%20NGO%20partners%20to%20implement%20the%20programme%20in%20selected%20schools%2C%20committing%20to%20support%20these%20schools%20for%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20years.%20The%20initiative%20works%20on%20dual%20fronts%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20training%20to%20teachers%20in%20STEM%20education%20and%20building%20physical%20infrastructure%20in%20schools%2C%20including%20STEM%20labs%20or%20digital%20classrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20begins%20with%20L%26amp%3BT%20selecting%20a%20school%2C%20and%20conducting%20an%20orientation%20and%20a%20needs%20assessment.%20A%20key%20criterion%20is%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20science%20teacher%2C%20and%20the%20initiative%20is%20tailored%20for%20students%20in%20Classes%206%20to%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20through%20NGO%20partners%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20delivers%20training%20to%20the%20district%20education%20officer%2C%20school%20principal%2C%20and%20teachers.%20Quarterly%20training%20sessions%20are%20conducted%20for%20teachers%2C%20with%20an%20observer%20present%20in%20the%20classroom%20to%20evaluate%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20teaching%20and%20provide%20guidance%20on%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20hands-on%20approach%20not%20only%20equips%20teachers%20to%20impart%20knowledge%20effectively%20but%20also%20strives%20to%20establish%20a%20sustainable%20model.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20empower%20teachers%20to%20continue%20delivering%20quality%20education%20independently%2C%20even%20without%20ongoing%20assistance%20from%20the%20NGO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20idea%20is%20to%20improve%20children%E2%80%99s%20conceptual%20understanding%20of%20science.%20Based%20on%20our%20observation%2C%20many%20students%20lose%20interest%20in%20science%20in%20Classes%206%20to%209.%20Girl%20students%20too%20face%20several%20biases%20and%20challenges%20as%20STEM%20courses%20are%20not%20traditionally%20considered%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20domain.%20If%20they%20get%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20scientific%20concepts%20through%20innovative%20methods%2C%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20of%20them%20choosing%20a%20career%20in%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Mabel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdapting%20to%20the%20specific%20needs%20and%20interests%20of%20each%20school%20management%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20enhances%20the%20physical%20infrastructure%20based%20on%20demand.%20What%20started%20with%2065%20schools%20has%20now%20expanded%20to%20include%20208%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeachers%20share%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20these%20models%20not%20only%20allows%20students%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340084%2Fgujarat-school-for-the-blind-and-visually-impaired-inclusive-design-architecture-by-anand-sonecha-sealabs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshowcase%20their%20creativity%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20aids%20teachers%20in%20delivering%20more%20effective%20explanations%2C%20utilising%20the%20visual%20aids%20provided%20by%20the%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20would%20just%20explain%20concepts%2C%20with%20children%20not%20being%20able%20to%20see%20how%20it%20works.%20Through%20these%20models%20and%20kits%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20how%20the%20concept%20works%2C%20helping%20in%20easier%20understanding.%20Children%20also%20ask%20more%20questions.%20The%20concept%20reaches%20them%20easily%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Veeramuthu%20N%2C%20a%20teacher%20from%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%2C%20Kaliannanpudur%2C%20Coimbatore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20L%26amp%3BT%20has%20provided%20them%20with%2075%20kits%2C%20which%20include%20working%20models%2C%20explanatory%20models%20and%20charts.%20Children%20are%20taken%20to%